{"obj_edit_time":"1706595411","blocks":[{"block_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","block_type":1,"children":["doxcn0UG90QeA4AZNmDTnrVIqGe","doxcnij4350NWjiojxAF8NvXgeg","Im5yd7oC8obJjAxAVE2cz3WVnBe","HDOEdcDN8oClS9xegJRcpiH1nU0","J3aLdQwc8odo2wxZexhcVlusnqf","doxcnSBh1VKkwzmhQ7iFVqLtk7c","doxcnURjU2HjqsAOKEZpB3yYZ7e","HuiEda1CSo4tvSx5q1TcuAASn5e","OFWCdtv1wonztnxonmZcLxl4nvb","Es3cdUmtPoJhfuxknQ5c198hn2e","QdXzdhonDoajtrxaOVDc1x9gnzc","KmLEd0VWfovmUZxkHwRcbylknSb","doxcnCl3QV6pYk82meKHgtD77md"],"page":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"基金管理-业务介绍","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1}},"parent_id":""},{"block_id":"doxcn0UG90QeA4AZNmDTnrVIqGe","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"概述","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"doxcnij4350NWjiojxAF8NvXgeg","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在证券市场，公募基金和私募基金是投资者广泛使用的两种主要投资工具。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"Im5yd7oC8obJjAxAVE2cz3WVnBe","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"公募基金由基金公司发行，向公众开放购买和赎回。这种基金的投资门槛相对较低，投资者可以通过证券交易所或基金销售机构购买。公募基金由专业的基金经理团队管理，投资者可以通过购买基金份额间接投资于股票、债券等资产，实现资产多样化和专业化管理。相对而言，私募基金则向特定投资者发行，投资门槛较高，且购买流程相对复杂。这种基金的运作方式更为灵活，通常包含更多的投资策略和市场环境，适用于机构投资者或个人高净值投资者。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"HDOEdcDN8oClS9xegJRcpiH1nU0","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"投资者参与基金投资的原因包括多方面考量。首先，基金投资可以帮助投资者分散风险。通过将资金投资于不同的资产类别和行业，投资者可以降低单一投资的风险，实现更稳健的投资组合。其次，基金由专业的基金经理团队管理，他们根据市场状况和基金的投资目标进行资产配置和交易，为投资者获取最佳回报。这种专业的管理可以减轻投资者的管理压力，并提高投资的效率和收益率。此外，购买基金相对简单方便，无需直接购买和管理股票或债券，基金公司会代为管理，为投资者提供了便利性和灵活性。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"J3aLdQwc8odo2wxZexhcVlusnqf","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"综上所述，基金投资为投资者提供了多样化、专业化的投资选择，使他们能够轻松参与市场并获得相应的投资回报。无论是公募基金还是私募基金，投资者都可以根据自身的需求和风险偏好选择适合的投资产品，并通过简单的购买和赎回流程参与市场，实现长期财富增长的目标。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"doxcnSBh1VKkwzmhQ7iFVqLtk7c","block_type":3,"heading1":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"基金管理步骤","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"doxcnURjU2HjqsAOKEZpB3yYZ7e","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"在基金业务中，券商主要执行以下关键步骤：","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}},{"block_id":"HuiEda1CSo4tvSx5q1TcuAASn5e","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"接受投资者的申购和赎回指令：客户在终端提交基金的申购和赎回的申请，券商需要接收客户指令同时冻结资金，根据业务规则汇总客户申赎的订单，生成基金文件。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"OFWCdtv1wonztnxonmZcLxl4nvb","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"提交基金文件至上手，等待基金公司确认：操作人员在基金管理后台核对生成的基金订单，将申赎数据发送给上手，等待基金公司返回份额和金额信息。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"Es3cdUmtPoJhfuxknQ5c198hn2e","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"回填订单数据：收到基金公司文件，回填基金净值、申购份额、赎回金额等信息，并核对确认。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"QdXzdhonDoajtrxaOVDc1x9gnzc","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"申赎交割：人工/自动进行申购交割、赎回货交割、赎回钱交割，系统根据申购订单扣取客户资金，增加客户的基金份额持仓；根据赎回订单扣取客户份额，返回客户资金。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"KmLEd0VWfovmUZxkHwRcbylknSb","block_type":13,"ordered":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"完成交割，通知客户：后台人员将通过银行与基金託管人交收资金，生成基金交易结单发送至客户。","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}},"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf"},{"block_id":"doxcnCl3QV6pYk82meKHgtD77md","block_type":2,"parent_id":"AllGd92k1o7MckxHYfpcnqLcnKf","text":{"elements":[{"text_run":{"content":"","text_element_style":{"bold":false,"inline_code":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false}}}],"style":{"align":1,"folded":false}}}]}